high_descs: Turn right and go to the blue trash can on the left of the toilet.
Pick up the green water bottle out of the trash can.
Move back and over to the right near the toilet tank.
Place the water bottle on the toilet tank on the left side.
Turn right and move towards the cabinet above the toilet.
Remove the green water bottle from the cabinet on the right.
Move over left to the toilet tank.
Place the water bottle on the right of the first water bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two water bottles on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Walk to the blue bin in between the toilet and the sink.
Pick up the container from the blue bin.
Move to face the back of the toilet.
Put the container down on the back of the toilet to the left of the tube.
Look up at the cabinet above the toilet.
Open the cabinet door on the right, take out the container. close the door.
Move to face the back of the toilet again.
Put the container down on the back of the toilet to the right of the container.
anns.task_desc: To move two containers to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Take a step to the right and look down to face the trash can on the floor.
Pick up the container in the trash can.
Look up to face the back of the toilet.
Place the container on the back of the toilet.
Look up to face the cabinet above the toilet.
Pick up the container in the cabinet above the toilet.
Look down to face the back of the toilet.
Place the container on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: To move two containers to the back of the toilet.
